<br />
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Here's a few tips to get you thinking</h2>
<p>As ever, <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy's</a> a great choice because there's so much variety there. The <a data-udi="umb://document/3848018580784607a13363dd2dd1885d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3848018580784607a13363dd2dd1885d}" title="Italy Lake Holidays">Italian lakes</a> have lots of little towns to explore, the scenery is so pretty in the sunshine, plus the food and drink is of course, amazing.</p>
<p>Try the <a data-udi="umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496}" title="The Dolomites">Dolomites</a> if you want some help working up an appetite - we think the mountains are some of the most beautiful to walk in.</p>
<p>Speaking of walking - <a data-udi="umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760}" title="Austria">Austria</a> should be on your list if you want to give your boots a proper outing, but <a data-udi="umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049}" title="Slovenia">Slovenia</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/baf439b4f3004bcdbcf23a91adb08ac5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/baf439b4f3004bcdbcf23a91adb08ac5}" title="Germany">Germany</a> are strong contenders too if you want somewhere a little different.</p>
<p>If scenery and discovery get you excited, try <a data-udi="umb://document/286d71b6bae94f84a7ac63448c015f54" href="/{localLink:umb://document/286d71b6bae94f84a7ac63448c015f54}" title="Norway">Norway</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/034b02ad431f4de8b15f328605d821cb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/034b02ad431f4de8b15f328605d821cb}" title="Iceland">Iceland</a> - they're simply like nowhere else in the world. Every time we get a chance to go, we take it.</p>
<p>Check out <a data-udi="umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf}" title="France">France</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a> for more summer playgrounds, or you could head further to <a data-udi="umb://document/4770458f947b44778e051efba30c7546" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4770458f947b44778e051efba30c7546}" title="Canada">Canada</a> for a truly memorable time.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a name="backtotop"></a><strong>Start exploring </strong></h2>
<br /><br />
<div class="g6">
