</div>
<div class="g6">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Tour the best of Europe &amp; Canada</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/731184fa7b9742f0a969771e90773289" href="/{localLink:umb://document/731184fa7b9742f0a969771e90773289}" title="Tours and Multi-Centre Holidays"><img src="/media/13081526/tour.jpg" alt="Tours and Multi Centres" data-udi="umb://media/a422190e49344d5d8b05f4cc05a15add" /></a></p>
